[[Translation:en/Manual/Refit]]
To refit your vehicle, it has to be in the depot.

In the vehicle screen, click on the third buton (a pair of boxes).


A screen will pop-up, to show the refit-options for that vehicle.

Click on the desired new type of cargo to carry.

In the bottom of the screen the costs and the amount of cargo is specified.


Click on the 'refit vehicle' button to refit.

A amount of cash is spend, and your vehicle is ready to move his '''new''' cargo type.

